{"tid":62431,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"高雄男被嫌J細 陰莖注填充物險變太監","createTime":"2017-01-01T01:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T09:30:25.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19955b98b2edd2859367c21c9b4412581fa74898","tid":62431,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:06:21.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=fuRBgXXYzUAJ6o7W790DaJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=dc3cc5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】高雄一名20多歲男子，與女網友發生一夜情後，被女方嘲笑陰莖短小，竟同意讓女方在陰莖注射填充物。隔日男子發現陰莖變黑，於是急忙求醫，有醫生最初建議男子切除陰莖，後來男子轉往長庚醫院，經多次手術，最終保住子孫根。<br />\n<br />\n高雄長庚醫院整外醫生楊家森表示，男子來到醫院時，陰莖像被一層瀝青包裹着，包皮經已全部壞死，而注射的填充物亦已滲進睪丸。原本其他醫院建議男子切掉陰莖保命，後來經過長庚醫院多次手術清創壞死包皮與潰爛組織，並移植其大腿皮膚到陰莖，把「腿皮換包皮」，才讓男子免於「截肢」。<br />\n<br />\n楊家森指腿皮延展性不及包皮，叮嚀男子出院後，勤練勃起陰莖作為康復治療。男子日前覆診，移植的腿皮已跟陰莖處融合，男子則表示手術初癒後，陰莖勃起時感到綁緊和痛楚，但隨着勃起次數增加，痛楚感覺經已減輕。"},{"pid":"3f7422cf423f8b8e6d392e9c288e501eb933f990","tid":62431,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4d3b2dbf99b3a4400916f723925ddcf238388c","tid":62431,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"都是jj惹的禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8027e4913e2cebfb76a9452a8a2fefefcd67b789","tid":62431,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746cf9711efdb3c0a9a0ab69745b3b9e982aba38","tid":62431,"uid":46373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"咁即係幾細條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ac64fa762044ddcec04a7c51b3d25406921a3d","tid":62431,"uid":24010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"372db9bb844ce254695c8cb0f86507479bec8ff8","tid":62431,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:30:25.000Z","msg":"有無告尻個台妹"}]}